{"tid":217639,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國球迷舉「殲英犬滅港毒」横額挑釁 港球迷反罵「支那狗」","createTime":"2017-04-26T02:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T03:55:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02b22d21da6f30ac5b990669358a07d063c4c4b8","tid":217639,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170425/large/1493131549_349e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170425%2Flarge%2F1493131549_349e.jpg&h=6679c071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東方龍獅今晚在旺角場上演的亞冠盃G組最後一場主場賽事，東方主場以0:6予廣州恒大，無緣晉級分組賽。賽事期間有恒大球迷向東方球迷方向舉中指，至賽事尾聲，恒大球迷舉「殲英犬 滅港毒」横額挑釁，部分香港球迷大叫「支那狗」還擊。<br />\n<br />\n初次入場觀賽的殷小姐指，東方今場已盡力，認為球場內氣氛很好，但見到恆大有球迷舉起反港獨標語，感到氣氛被政治化，「埋門就拉起，體育唔應該咁掛勾」。<br />\n<br />\n球迷葉先生認為東方今場輸得較預期多，因東方與恆大在技術水平上有分野，「人哋財大氣粗，入波嘅都係外援啫」，惟他認為東方今場踢得較保守，應更放膽進攻。亞冠盃三次東方主場都有入場觀賽的他說，今場氣氛最激烈，「但唔係完全專注喺運動，有少少政治化」。<br />\n<br />\n球迷潘先生指，無預想過東方會勝出，東方今場表現中規中矩，「打逆境波梗係難踢&hellip;&hellip;個教練都可能冇諗過守唔住」，又認為今日落雨，對球員體能較辛苦。他指，今場兩對球迷氣氛激烈，恆大球迷較有組織性，相信香港球迷如組織得更好，氣氛會更熱烈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56613316&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56613316%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170425&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=16c39e1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56613316%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170425&h=a22e7809\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56613316&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170425</a>"},{"pid":"1d18f4e289c323ed8561cff6eca42b447079fab4","tid":217639,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/119FrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F119FrZ.jpg&h=e4e8e338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等睇雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8a41ba1993ab0a2988b1b125564008a76d81ee","tid":217639,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ac28fc506d8180c5599ea1f831fabbd53b7db44","tid":217639,"uid":6942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:55:47.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}